OVERVIEW
Wazuh is a robust security monitoring solution designed for threat detection, compliance management, and incident response. Built on open-source principles, Wazuh integrates with popular tools such as the Elastic Stack and provides a centralized platform for monitoring, analyzing, and visualizing security events. It is widely used by security professionals to identify anomalies, detect potential intrusions, and ensure regulatory compliance.

FEATURES
1. Intrusion Detection – Monitor log data and detect suspicious activities in real time.
2. Log Data Analysis – Collect and analyze logs from various sources to identify potential security breaches.
3. File Integrity Monitoring – Track and alert on unauthorized changes to critical files.
4. Vulnerability Detection – Assess system vulnerabilities and provide remediation recommendations.
5. Compliance Monitoring – Support regulatory compliance with built-in checks and automated reporting.
6. Configuration Assessment – Evaluate system configurations to ensure best security practices.
7. Alerting & Reporting – Generate real-time alerts and detailed reports for incident response and forensic investigations.
8.Scalability & Flexibility – Easily scale to accommodate large environments and customize dashboards to suit organizational needs.

Wazuh is an essential platform for IT security teams, enabling proactive defense measures and continuous monitoring of the security posture across on-premises, cloud, and hybrid environments.
